  <brief_title>Evaluate the Effects of Patupilone on the Pharmacokinetics of Midazolam and Omeprazole in Patients With Advanced Malignancies (Extension)</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label Phase I Study to Evaluate the Effects of Patupilone on the Pharmacokinetics of Midazolam and Omeprazole in Patients With Advanced Malignancies (Extension)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
